This is a simple example of rest-api

the url_prefix api is: /app/v1/
It count with some endpoints which are:

---

This endpoint is used to create an account

method: post
host:port/app/v1/signup
info:
json with:
username
email
password

---

---

This endpoint is used to login in the api

method: get
host:port/app/v1/login
info:
json with:
email
password

method: get,patch
host:port/app/v1/user

---

---

This endpoint is used to show the list of users

method: get
info:
args with:
token

This endpoint is used to update the user information

method: patch
info:
args with:
token
json with:
username
email
password

---
